Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是羊寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命地啾啪啾啪啾啪啾啪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吸媽媽的奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神地在吸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是小豬豬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  在搶媽媽的乳頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是Animal  Video?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員列隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然來到了這裡  你們就不再是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是地上最卑劣的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你們能正常接客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會以最嚴厲的方面鍛鍊你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的挫折和脫隊就是我們的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  菜鳥們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話的前後要加上Sir  知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir  是  Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Sir  Yes  Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir  Yes  Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir  Yes  Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的幹勁不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人員又要減少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你來殺雞儆猴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意忘形了  你這囓齒類
